@@TJvCommonDialog
Summary
  Base class for all common dialogs that return a Boolean result to indicate if the dialog was
  canceled or not.
Description
  TJvCommonDialog is the base class for all common dialogs that return a Boolean result to indicate
  if the dialog was canceled or not.
  
  The Execute method will return False if the dialog was canceled. Otherwise True will be returned.
See Also
  TJvCommonDialogP
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialog.Execute
Summary
  Displays the dialog.
Description
  Execute will show the common dialog. The function returns False if the dialog was canceled or True
  if it was not canceled.
